Possible Natural Gas Hoax Forwarded by John D Williamson on AM To cc John D NDERSEN WO Date AM From Subject Possible Natural Gas Hoax With all the fear going around I feel I should warn you of a possible scaretactic I have heard of that might occur on April of next year I have a friend who has a friend who dates his cousin who has a contact at a company where a guy has a friend who knows someone who trades natural gas basis Apparently this person went to Sullivans in Houston the other night and overheard a story that shivered my timbers He said that he heard some well dressed guys talking in hushed tones about natural gas prices He overheard that there was a rumor going around at one of the guys offices that a gas trader there has a friend who heard this story from a scheduler who knows a power trader who dates a lease crude buyer who has a cousin who works in accounting at a publicly traded company that does business with a pinto bean grower in South Texas Apparently on April st some strangers will be going around with their index finger pointed out of a closed fist They may look like they are pointing the finger They may approach you for assistance with their finger DO NOT PULL THEIR FINGER This may or may not be real but I am sending it out to those I care about The only thing we have to fearis fear itself said Franklin Delano Roosevelt Internet Email My lifeWay too close to home Male Maturity When I was I hoped that one day I would have a girlfriend When I was I got a girlfriend but there was no passion So I decided I needed a passionate girl with a zest for life In college I dated a passionate girl but she was too emotional Everything was an emergency she was a drama queen cried all the time and threatened suicide So I decided I needed a girl with stability When I was I found a very stable girl but she was boring She was totally predictable and never got excited about anything Life became so dull that I decided that I needed a girl with some excitement When I was I found an exciting girl but I couldnt keep up with her She rushed from one thing to another never settling on anything She did mad impetuous things and made me miserable as often as happy She was great fun initially and very energetic but directionless So I decided to find a girl with some real ambition When I turned I found a smart ambitious girl with her feet planted firmly on the ground and married her She was so ambitious that she divorced me and took everything I owned Now I am and just looking for a girl with big tits Internet Email Confidentiality Footer PrivilegedConfidential Information may be contained in this message If you are not the addressee indicated in this message or responsible for delivery of the message to such person you may not copy or deliver this message to anyone In such case you should destroy this message and kindly notify the sender by reply email Please advise immediately if you or your employer do not consent to Internet email for messages of this kind Opinions conclusions and other information in this message that do not relate to the official business of my firm shall be understood as neither given nor endorsed by it
